The subtree under avatar/liveavatar/ is copied VERBATIM and PINNED (not a submodule), per the
project decision to own and pin the inference code. Our additions live alongside it:
    avatar/avatar_worker.py   — resident streaming driver (NEW; implements get_audio_callback,
                                drives the block-wise generator, emits frames over IPC)
    avatar/idle.py            — idle audio + idle frame ring (NEW)
    avatar/blend.py           — idle<->talk crossfade (NEW)
    avatar/ipc_worker.py      — ZeroMQ transport for rank 4 (NEW)

Modifications to vendored files, if any, are noted inline with a "# LIVEAVATAR-FORK:" comment.
